eSourceHighlight version
========================

![Screenshot to eSourceHighlight](https://github.com/MaxPerl/eSourceHighlight/blob/main/screenshot.jpg?raw=1 "Screenshot to eSourceHighlight")

A simple text editor (frontend to the gnu source-highlight library) for not to heavy files developed with Perl/pEFL.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Syntax::SourceHighlight
  pEFL
  File::HomeDir

